        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3243811631" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17442544454931357618">These are my honest views: <br/><br/>I have ensured not to include any spoilers. <br/><br/>This was truly a moving and intense read. The shifting stories and perspectives helped shape this story into a touching and intriguing novel. <br/><br/>Kiran Bhat has created a novel where I feel it has one central purpose- to show us the reality of the world we live in where we aren’t so different and are only divided by society. We can relate to one another if we tried hard enough to do so. <br/><br/>This novel is beautifully written and is po</span>
  <span id="freeText17442544454931357618" style="display:none">These are my honest views: <br /><br />I have ensured not to include any spoilers. <br /><br />This was truly a moving and intense read. The shifting stories and perspectives helped shape this story into a touching and intriguing novel. <br /><br />Kiran Bhat has created a novel where I feel it has one central purpose- to show us the reality of the world we live in where we aren’t so different and are only divided by society. We can relate to one another if we tried hard enough to do so. <br /><br />This novel is beautifully written and is poetic. For me, this stream of consciousness and lyrical nature is awe-inspiring and draws the reader in. <br /><br />We see the difference in a tribal environment to a more modern city and this shows that we can be so different in lifestyle and culture, yet we are united in our existence- being human. <br /><br />I will be telling all my friends to give this book a chance. <br /><br />A great read and I would highly recommend! </span>
  <a data-text-id="17442544454931357618" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

