        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3258058360" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2225737092770277052">This was a pleasant different type story for me, which is to say I usually read action, adventure, mystery, suspense, and thriller. I enjoyed it because it was different from my normal selection. The book unfolds with many narrations, but focuses on a few. The places and persons parallel our own and show us how our lives are intertwined from impoverished towns and villages, to modern cities. They face the same complexities we do, and character challenges and developments are easily related in th</span>
  <span id="freeText2225737092770277052" style="display:none">This was a pleasant different type story for me, which is to say I usually read action, adventure, mystery, suspense, and thriller. I enjoyed it because it was different from my normal selection. The book unfolds with many narrations, but focuses on a few. The places and persons parallel our own and show us how our lives are intertwined from impoverished towns and villages, to modern cities. They face the same complexities we do, and character challenges and developments are easily related in this book. <br /><br />The author writes with imagination and the story can be page-turning at times. I highly recommend it for people who enjoy stories involving character and life challenges.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2225737092770277052" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3258058360">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link3258058360" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=3258058360&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F49005456-we-of-the-forsaken-world">flag</a>





